videos.description: Senior Corey Davis Jr. scores 9 of Houston's first 11 points, including a floater in transition.
videos.headline: Houston's Davis crosses over and gets floater to fall

videos.description: Houston's Breaon Brady delivers a behind-the-back pass to Galen Robinson Jr. for an easy layup.
videos.headline: Behind-the-back pass leads to Houston layup

videos.description: Cincinnati's Nysier Brooks grabs an offensive rebound and slams it home, but is called for a technical foul for taunting.
videos.headline: Cincy's Brooks called for technical following dunk

videos.description: Cincinnati's Jarron Cumberland buries a deep 3-pointer to cut into Houston's second-half lead.
videos.headline: Cincy's Cumberland knocks down 3-pointer
